data.description: NEW ROOF IS COMING! TAKE ADVANTAGE OF ASSUMING THE SELLER FHA MORTGAGE AT HIGHLY FAVORABLE 3.125% INTEREST RATE! What a great find! Amazing opportunity to own this lovely 3 bedrooms, 2 bath home with 1,850 sq.ft, located in the Highland Oaks community nestled in the rolling hills of Minneola. As you enter through the front door, the home welcomes you with a formal living room and a den/office/flexible space. Immediate attention is drawn to the vaulted ceilings in the kitchen/family room, which enhances its spacious look. The kitchen is equipped with plenty of cabinet and counter space, closet pantry, breakfast bar, that opens to an adjacent dining space. The home offers an excellent layout and flow, with split floor plan and ample room sizes. The spacious owner’s suite is complemented with two walk-in closet, garden tub, private water closet, separate shower, his/her separate vanities. This home is complete with a two cars garage and a good size full fenced backyard. Water heater 2020, A/C 2021, Fence 2020. Conveniently located only minutes from Hwy 27, easy access to the Florida Turnpike, shopping, dining. Schedule a showing today!
